org.apache.karaf.shell.commands

Interface Action

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.felix.gogo.commands.Action
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface Action
extends org.apache.felix.gogo.commands.Action
    An action allows to easily execute commands in karaf. It can be assumed that each action is only accessed by a single thread at a time. An Action is always part of an AbstractCommand. The AbstractCommand makes sure the single threaded assumption above is true. Before the call to the execute method the action is checked for annotated fields (@Argument, @Option). These fields are populated from the command arguments before the action is called. Any class implementing Action must have a no argument constructor. This is necessary so the help generator can instantiate the class and get the default values.
Often called with List. Shall be called with DisplayException, ProfileCopy, LoadTest, NamesCommand, UninstallKarCommand, ProfileList, ListUsersCommand, DefaultActionPreparator, WatchAction, ListGroupsCommand, DumpCommand, ProfileDelete, EventDisplayCommand, SshAction, CancelCommand, ProfileRename, ListAction, ObrCommandSupport, GetLogLevel, ScheduleScript, ListRealmsCommand, BundlesCommand, UnbindCommand, SystemProperty, UninstallAction, Name, LogoutAction, Stop, ConfigCommandSupport, ProfileEdit, ListPendingCommand, SshServerAction, ScheduleCommand, JavaAction, Start, ProxyAddCommand, ThreadsAction, FindClass, DeleteCommand, PrintStackTracesAction, ClearLog, ServletListCommand, RegionInfoCommand, InstanceCommandSupport, FeaturesCommandSupport, LogEntry, PrintfAction, BundleCommand, ContextsCommand, Trigger, Wait, Install, StartLevel, ProfileChangeParents, StartAction, CreateKarCommand, InstallCommand, EventSendCommand, Exports, Imports, ProxyRemoveCommand, ManageRealmCommand, FrameworkOptions, StopAction, EventTailCommand, WhoamiCommand, ProxyListCommand, LogTail, Reschedule, ListKarCommand, InfoAction, RequirementList, Launch, UpdateCommand, Shutdown, DisplayLog, SuCommand, Watch, InstallAction, JaasCommandSupport, SetLogLevel, SudoCommand, ExecuteAction, BindCommand, ListServices, CreateCommand, SourceAction, Unschedule, CompletionAction, InstallKarCommand, ProfileCreate.
